TITLE: Hide Other Shipping Methods When Free Shipping Available
DESCRIPTION: PHP function that filters shipping rates to only show free shipping when it's available. Uses the woocommerce_package_rates filter to modify available shipping methods.
SOURCE: https://github.com/woocommerce/woocommerce/blob/trunk/docs/code-snippets/free_shipping_customization.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
/**
 * Hide other shipping rates when free shipping is available.
 *
 * @param array $rates Array of rates found for the package.
 *
 * @return array
 */
function fsc_hide_shipping_rates_when_free_is_available( $rates ) {
	// Go through each rate found.
	foreach ( $rates as $rate_id => $rate ) {
		// If Free Shipping is found, define it as the only rate and break out of the foreach.
		if ( 'free_shipping' === $rate->method_id ) {
			$rates = [ $rate_id => $rate ];
			break;
		}
	}
	return $rates;
}
add_filter( 'woocommerce_package_rates', 'fsc_hide_shipping_rates_when_free_is_available', 10, 1 );
```

