TITLE: Defining WooCommerce Cart and Checkout Document Schema in JSON
DESCRIPTION: Specifies the complete JSON Schema definition for the WooCommerce 'document object'. It outlines the structure, data types, descriptions, and constraints for properties within the `cart`, `checkout`, and `customer` objects, including nested structures like `totals` and `address`. This schema is used to validate the structure of the document object and serves as the basis for defining conditional logic for checkout fields.
