TITLE: Implementing BEM Naming Convention in WooCommerce CSS
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the proper implementation of BEM (Block Element Modifier) methodology in WooCommerce CSS, including examples of blocks, nested blocks, elements, and modifiers. All classes are prefixed with 'woocommerce-' to prevent conflicts with WordPress core and other plugins.
