LANGUAGE: css
CODE:
```
/* Block */
.woocommerce-loop {}

/* Nested block */
.woocommerce-loop-product {}

/* Modifier */
.woocommerce-loop-product--sale {}

/* Element */
.woocommerce-loop-product__link {}

/* Element */
.woocommerce-loop-product__button-add-to-cart {}

/* Modifier */
.woocommerce-loop-product__button-add-to-cart--added {}
```

