TITLE: Updating WordPress to Nightly Build in E2E Initialization Script
DESCRIPTION: Example ad-hoc Bash initialization script designed to be passed as a parameter to `wc-e2e docker:up`. This script performs standard setup tasks (activating WooCommerce, theme, user creation, plugin installation) and additionally updates WordPress to the latest nightly point release using the WordPress Beta Tester plugin and WP-CLI.
