TITLE: WooCommerce CRUD Save Method
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of the save method in WC_Data class, handling both creation and updates of WooCommerce objects.
SOURCE: https://github.com/woocommerce/woocommerce/blob/trunk/docs/data-management/crud-objects.md#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
public function save() {
	if ( $this->data_store ) {
		do_action( 'woocommerce_before_' . $this->object_type . '_object_save', $this, $this->data_store );

		if ( $this->get_id() ) {
			$this->data_store->update( $this );
		} else {
			$this->data_store->create( $this );
		}
		return $this->get_id();
	}
}
```

