TITLE: Querying Order Currencies in MySQL
DESCRIPTION: SQL query to retrieve order IDs, names, types, and currencies from WordPress database tables.
SOURCE: https://github.com/woocommerce/woocommerce/blob/trunk/docs/reporting/extending-woocommerce-admin-reports.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT
    ID,
    post_name,
    post_type,
    currency_postmeta.meta_value AS currency
FROM `wp_posts`
JOIN wp_postmeta currency_postmeta ON wp_posts.ID = currency_postmeta.post_id
WHERE currency_postmeta.meta_key = '_order_currency'
ORDER BY wp_posts.post_date DESC
LIMIT 3
```

